==German==
===Etymology===
Believed to derive from an old children's game called ''Rumpele stilt oder der Poppart'', which was mentioned in [[w:Johann Fischart|Johann Fischart]]'s ''Geschichtklitterung, or [[Gargantua]]'' of 1577, a loose adaptation of [[w:Rabelais|Rabelais]]' [[w:Gargantua and Pantagruel|Gargantua and Pantagruel]].
===Proper noun===
